'''Dobido''' was the smaller of [[Sernpidal/Legends|Sernpidal's]] two [[Moon/Legends|moons]]. It measured twenty [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] in diameter and was covered with large cities all over the surface.

==History==
The [[Praetorite Vong]], employing the [[Yo'gand's Core]] tactic, used a [[dovin basal]] to pull it into Sernpidal, destroying both. Millions, including the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]], were killed when Dobido collided with the [[Planet/Legends|planet]], stripping its atmosphere and smashing much of Sernpidal's northern hemisphere loose.<ref name="Atlas">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

